WEBVTT

00:03.501 --> 00:06.918
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:08.169 --> 00:11.408
- Oh, no.
- What's wrong, Mr Peterson?

00:11.586 --> 00:14.367
It's my anniversary, I have nothing
for Vera, and stores are closed.

00:15.663 --> 00:17.483
Normie's in big trouble now.

00:17.662 --> 00:19.817
Will Mrs Peterson
give you the cold shoulder?

00:19.996 --> 00:23.815
It's not the cold shoulder I mind.
It's the hard knee.

00:24.776 --> 00:26.406
Well, not to worry there, Norm.

00:26.574 --> 00:28.271
I think with your wit
and resourcefulness,

00:28.439 --> 00:30.806
you'll come up with a suitable gift.

00:31.488 --> 00:33.185
Yeah.

00:33.353 --> 00:35.754
You're absolutely right, Cliffie.

00:37.898 --> 00:40.042
I tried. I'm doomed.

00:41.014 --> 00:42.678
I know where there's
a gas station open.

00:42.845 --> 00:45.414
Why don't you get her
a can of 40-weight.

00:45.593 --> 00:47.380
- Very funny.
- Hey, why not give her

00:47.547 --> 00:50.037
the best gift of all, Mr Peterson?

00:50.216 --> 00:51.958
A night of romance.

00:52.126 --> 00:54.538
Carla, where's that gas station at?

00:55.376 --> 00:57.866
Come on. Come on, Norm.
You can do better than that.

00:58.045 --> 01:00.033
- What?
- That ashtray's better than that.

01:00.211 --> 01:02.278
Come on, man.

01:02.668 --> 01:04.566
Ashtray, huh?

01:06.410 --> 01:08.442
It's a little shoddy, but...

01:08.621 --> 01:11.402
You know, with a nice pack
of cigarettes or something,

01:11.994 --> 01:15.400
a nice snappy new pack of matches,
I think we got something here.

01:15.567 --> 01:17.555
- Hey, hey, hey, Norm!
- Does Vera even smoke?

01:17.734 --> 01:20.135
Oh, yeah, she's been
known to smoke.

01:20.314 --> 01:22.190
Occasionally after sex.

01:22.357 --> 01:24.390
Usually during.

