23:07.631 --> 23:11.294
Hey, I came pretty darn close
a couple of times, didn't l?

23:14.041 --> 23:16.867
That's not what I meant.

23:20.787 --> 23:22.328
You were wonderful.

23:22.786 --> 23:25.321
Yeah, you were
pretty wonderful yourself.

23:26.829 --> 23:30.570
- It can be so wonderful, can't it, Sam?
- You bet.

23:32.111 --> 23:35.350
Thank God there's no danger
of all of that starting up again.

23:35.528 --> 23:38.689
Right. We know what kind of hell
that would lead to.

23:39.482 --> 23:41.548
Amen.

23:56.960 --> 23:59.115
Will there be anything else?

24:00.623 --> 24:03.538
